Dear {clientName},

This email is to formally submit invoice #{invoiceNumber} dated {invoiceDate} for your review and payment processing.

INVOICE SUMMARY:
Invoice Number: {invoiceNumber}
Issue Date: {invoiceDate}
Total Amount Due: ${totalAmount}
