Dear {clientName},

This is a friendly reminder about invoice #{invoiceNumber} issued on {invoiceDate}.

Payment Details:
- Invoice: #{invoiceNumber}
- Amount: ${totalAmount}
- Due Date: {dueDate}
- Status: Payment Pending

We appreciate your prompt attention to this matter. The invoice is attached for your convenience.

If payment has already been sent, please disregard this reminder. Otherwise, please arrange payment at your earliest convenience.

Thank you for your business.

Best regards,
{companyName}
